{"type":"message","id":"61164a74","parentId":"ee6cb842","timestamp":"2026-05-20T19:54:58.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, `e588` is NOT `切`. Let me figure out what `e588` should be. The context is:\n- pos 519: `...e4 b8 3F 28 e4 bd 3f 73 72 63 2e 2a...` => `...中(?e4bd?src.*)`\n  - This is the comment: `# 确保项目根目录在 sys.path 中(保证 src.* 导入始终可用)`\n  - Wait, 保 is E4 BF 9D. But prefix is E4 BD.\n  \nLooking at the raw hex around position 519, I'm seeing `...e4 b8 3f 28 e4 bd 3f 73 72 63...` which decodes to `...中(? (?src.*` — so both `e4b8` and `e4bd` are corrupted to `3F`. The character `中` should be `e4 b8 ad`, but the third byte got corrupted to `3f`. So the original text was probably `确保项目根目录在 sys.path 中(保证 src.* 导入始终可用)`, where both the third byte of `中` and the third byte of `保` were damaged. I'm tracing through the hex encoding to verify the character mappings — checking that each 3-byte sequence correctly decodes to the expected Chinese characters, starting with 确, 保, 项, and working through to sys.path. 我在追踪注释文本中的编码问题——看起来 `中` 和 `保` 后面的字节都被损坏成了 `?`，导致后面的 `保` 变成了 `bd 3f` 而不是正确的 `bf 9d`。我意识到 `e58c` 是 `初` 的前缀，而 `e588` 应该对应另一个字符——从\"初始化\"这个词来看，`初` 的编码确实是 `e5 88 9d`，所以我需要修正映射关系，确保 `e588` 指向正确的字符。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7900701a621c427fb74ffa73","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\n# Fix mapping: e58c is NOT 初. Let me verify\n初 = '初'.encode('utf-8').hex()\nprint(f'初 = {初}')  # e5889d\n\n# So e588 -> 初 (0x9D), and e58c -> ?\n# Let me find what character has prefix e58c\nimport struct\nfor cp in range(0x5200, 0x5260):\n    try:\n        b = chr(cp).encode('utf-8')\n        if b[:2].hex() == 'e58c':\n            print(f'U+{cp:04X} = {chr(cp)} = {b.hex()}')\n    except:\n        pass\n\n# And also verify e58c matches 化\n化 = '化'.encode('utf-8').hex()\nprint(f'化 = {化}')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"YerPlan","model":"qwen3.6-plus","usage":{"input":33823,"output":704,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34527,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779306883135,"responseId":"msg_ebf09b8c-3b16-4170-bdb3-ca4e6095ae36"}}
